//================visibility : visible;hidden ===
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
	<style type="text/css">
		
	div
	{
		width:100px;
		height: 70px;
		background-color: yellow;
		border: 3px solid red;
		color:red;
	}
	.aa
	{
		visibility: hidden;
	}

	div h1
	{
		visibility: visible;
	}

	</style>
</head>
<body>

	<div class="aa">	
	    <h1> menu1</h1>    
	</div>
	
</body>
</html>
//==============display: none; inline,block,inline-block===========
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title></title>
	<style type="text/css">
		
	div p#myid1
	{
		width:100px;
		height: 70px;
		background-color: yellow;
		border: 3px solid red;
		color:red;
//		display: none;
//		display: inline;
//		display: block;
		display: inline-block;
	}
	</style>
</head>
<body>

	<div>
	
Video provides a powerful way to help you prove your point.<p id="myid1"> Hello world </p>When you click Online Video, you can paste in the embed code for the video you want to add. You can also type a keyword to search online for the video that best fits your document.   
	</div>
	
</body>
</html>
